Notable Locations.Hills & Peaks:
* [[Icespire Peak]], the tallest peak of the Sword Mountains.
* [[Scaleblight Summit]], the location of a Netherese [[Mythallar]].
* [[Mount Galardrym]], the peak that was home to the dwarves of [[Clan Forgebar]].{{Cite dragon/252/Wyrms of the North: Palarandusk|70}}
* [[Mount Sar]], the second-most southern of the range's peaks, which was named after a legendary [[fomorian]].{{Cite web enhancement/Environs of Waterdeep|14}}
* [[Mount Helimbrar]], the southernmost peak of the mountains was home to the underground stronghold of the [[Shadow Thief]] [[Marune]].
* [[Umbrage Hill]], a foothill near [[Phandalin]], west of [[Icespire Peak]].
